text: Myaree is a suburb of Perth, Western Australia, located within the City of Melville. Myaree gets its name from an Aboriginal word meaning foliage. Myaree is a predominantly light industrial area. When it was developed, roads were named after soldiers killed in World War I and early settlers in the area. ==References== Category:Suburbs of Perth, Western Australia Category:Suburbs in the City of Melville
title: Myaree, Western Australia
